PN,41101
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FSir Chris Bryant says his appointment
OL,8,Fas Northern Ireland Secretary is
OL,9,F"quite daunting" after he replaced
OL,10,F'gentleman' Hilary Benn.
OL,12,FOn the Executive parties' pleas for
OL,13,Ffunding, the Labour MP said he was in
OL,14,Fthe "Bette Midler" position.
OL,16,F"You've got to give a little, take a
OL,17,Flittle, let your poor heart break a
OL,18,Flittle," he told UTV.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FSir Chris replaced Hilary Benn as the
OL,8,FCabinet minister leading the Northern
OL,9,FIreland Office when Andy Burnham
OL,10,Fbecame Prime Minister on Monday.
OL,12,FSpeaking to UTV on Tuesday, the
OL,13,FSecretary of State paid tribute to his
OL,14,Fpredecessor and outlined his
OL,15,Fpriorities in the role.
OL,17,F"I'm always going to make an argument
OL,18,Ffor Northern Ireland," he said.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"I follow in phenomenal footsteps.
OL,8,FHilary Benn was, is one of the most
OL,9,Fgentlemanly gentlemen that there's
OL,10,Fever been in British politics, and I
OL,11,Fwant to pay tribute to him, but I know
OL,12,Fprecisely what he would say, which is,
OL,13,Fof course you always fight for the
OL,14,Fbest possible deal for Northern
OL,15,FIreland, that's my job."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FWhen pressed if he shared Hilary
OL,8,FBenn's position that the Northern
OL,9,FIreland Executive should agree a
OL,10,Fbudget while discussions with the
OL,11,FTreasury continue for extra funding,
OL,12,FSir Chris referenced the "Bette Midler
OL,13,Fposition".
OL,15,FHe added: "I mean, the truth is that
OL,16,Fpeople have got to sit down at the
OL,17,Ftable and negotiate. That's always
OL,18,Fwhat you've got to do.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"I'm very new in post. It's all quite
OL,8,Fdaunting in many ways because there
OL,9,Fare enormous responsibilities here.
OL,11,F"I represent one of the poorest areas
OL,12,Fin the UK in South Wales, and of
OL,13,Fcourse I want to make sure that the
OL,14,Ffuture of Northern Ireland is bright
OL,15,Fbecause it's about jobs and
OL,16,Fopportunity and economic prosperity,
OL,17,Fall of the things that we've just got
OL,18,Fto get right for Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"I know everybody always wants a
OL,8,Fcheque, that's one of the standard
OL,9,Fthings in British politics, but I'm
OL,10,Factually more interested in the
OL,11,Fchecklist.
OL,13,F"How do we get things right? How do we
OL,14,Fmake sure we've got more people into
OL,15,Fjobs, how do we make sure that all our
OL,16,Fpublic services are really working for
OL,17,Fthe people of Northern Ireland.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"How do we make sure that we've got
OL,8,Fthe money to be able to do the job,
OL,9,Fall of that together, but also how do
OL,10,Fwe look to a bigger horizon about
OL,11,Feconomic prosperity and opportunity
OL,12,Ffor the whole of Northern Ireland?"
OL,14,FSir Chris denied that the UK
OL,15,FGovernment's legacy legislation -
OL,16,Fwhich appears to have stalled - was in
OL,17,Flimbo.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"The bill is not in limbo. The bill is
OL,8,Fvery much in fine fettle. I look
OL,9,Fforward to taking it through the House
OL,10,Fof Commons later on this year."
OL,12,FSir Chris - who was a staunch remainer
OL,13,Fduring the Brexit referendum - was
OL,14,Fasked about comments made by TUV
OL,15,FLeader Jim Allister in response to his
OL,16,Fappointment as an "EU fanatic".
OL,18,F"I think there's a really good
OL,19,Fopportunity here, which is Northern
OL,20,FIreland is both in the single market
OL,21,Fand in the United Kingdom.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"That gives it a real set of
OL,8,Fopportunities to be able to develop
OL,9,Feconomic opportunity for people.
OL,11,F"I want every single young person to
OL,12,Fthink this is the place where I can
OL,13,Freally make the best future for me and
OL,14,Fmy family. Now, does that mean
OL,15,Fpoliticians wrangling all the time
OL,16,Fabout this, that and the other, in
OL,17,Fparticular about constitutional issues
OL,18,Fis going to sort that for people? I
OL,19,Fsuspect not."
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FIn phone calls on Tuesday morning, the
OL,8,Fnew prime minister told the leaders of
OL,9,FScotland, Wales and Northern Ireland
OL,10,Fhe was "focused on practical measures,
OL,11,Fnot constitutional changes like
OL,12,Ffurther referendum".
OL,14,FA Downing Street spokesperson said
OL,15,FAndy Burnham had calls with Scottish
OL,16,FFirst Minister John Swinney, Welsh
OL,17,FFirst Minister Rhun ap Iorwerth, and
OL,18,FMichelle O'Neill and Emma Little-
OL,19,FPengelly, the First Minister and
OL,20,Fdeputy First Minister of Northern
OL,21,FIreland.
OL,26,@rD@HOUtD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FThe spokesperson added: "The prime
OL,8,Fminister said he was serious about
OL,9,Fcreating a new politics ` rooted in
OL,10,Ffinding common ground based on
OL,11,Fcollaborative, practical and pragmatic
OL,12,Frelations with the heads of the
OL,13,Fdevolved governments.
OL,15,F"Working in partnership, the prime
OL,16,Fminister said together they could
OL,17,Fdrive deeper devolution to all parts
OL,18,Fof the United Kingdom to get growth
OL,19,Fgoing.
OL,26,@oD@YOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"The prime minister added he was
OL,8,Ffocused on practical measures, not
OL,9,Fconstitutional changes like further
OL,10,Freferendums, to give families more
OL,11,Fbreathing room by helping them with
OL,12,Fthe cost of living, which he had done
OL,13,Ftoday by helping millions of
OL,14,Fhouseholds with their energy bills.
OL,16,F"The prime minister said he looked
OL,17,Fforward to meeting with the heads of
OL,18,Fthe devolved governments soon and
OL,19,Fvisiting Scotland, Wales and Northern
OL,20,FIreland shortly."
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU|D@QO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FSinn Fein MP John Finucane said: "I
OL,8,Fdon't think anybody has called on Andy
OL,9,FBurnham to set the date for the
OL,10,Freferendum tomorrow or indeed next
OL,11,Fyear, we are asking them to recognise
OL,12,Fthis conversation is happening.
OL,26,@oD@Grr
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"We are asking him to resource and
OL,8,Finform that conversation because as he
OL,9,Fknows all too well, because he is now
OL,10,Fin charge of the mess that has evolved
OL,11,Ffrom Brexit, not to plan for a major
OL,12,Freferendum is a recipe for disaster,
OL,13,Fso he should play his part in making
OL,14,Fsure that that doesn't happen to
OL,15,Fpeople here."
OL,17,FDUP leader Gavin Robinson insisted
OL,18,FStormont parties cannot afford to
OL,19,F"restart" budget discussions with a
OL,20,Fnew Secretary of State.
OL,26,@{D@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G14/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FGavin Robinson said he hopes
OL,8,Fengagement with the newly appointed
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland Secretary will build
OL,10,Fon those already under way as
OL,11,FStormont's budget crisis continues.
OL,13,FSpeaking to reporters at CS Lewis
OL,14,FSquare in east Belfast, Mr Robinson
OL,15,Fadded he had "many exchanges" with the
OL,16,FRhondda and Ogmore MP, describing him
OL,17,Fas "good fun".
OL,26,@wD@NOUwD@]O]yD@DOUyD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41116
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"I think he's been clear about his
OL,8,Fdesire to see Northern Ireland's
OL,9,Fposition within the United Kingdom
OL,10,Fstrengthened, that is a good thing,
OL,11,Fthat is something that I welcome," he
OL,12,Fsaid.
OL,14,F"But he will know, and if he doesn't,
OL,15,Fhe will quickly learn that there are
OL,16,Fsome significant challenges that we
OL,17,Fneed to deal with in Northern Ireland,
OL,18,Fincluding financial stability."
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@bO]vD@AOUzD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41117
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FJust weeks ago, the parties met Mr
OL,8,FBenn at Hillsborough Castle as
OL,9,Fdevolved ministers have failed to
OL,10,Fagree a budget for the current
OL,11,Ffinancial year, with departments
OL,12,Foperating on contingency budgets since
OL,13,FApril.
OL,15,FMinisters have consistently made the
OL,16,Fpoint that they need more money from
OL,17,Fthe Treasury to address a funding
OL,18,Fcrisis facing public services in the
OL,19,Fregion.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41118
SC,0018
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FMr Robinson said he wants to "build on
OL,8,Fthe progress" of those discussions
OL,9,Fwith "a new prime minister, a new
OL,10,Fchancellor, and a new secretary of
OL,11,Fstate".
OL,13,FAsked if new personalities may disrupt
OL,14,Fthat momentum, he replied: "I don't
OL,15,Fthink we can afford to restart the
OL,16,Fdiscussions that we've already had."
OL,26,@oD@^OUpD@MO]qD@FOUsD@FO]vD@\OUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G18/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41119
SC,0019
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"The fact that we stand here today at
OL,8,Fthe back end of July and there's no
OL,9,Fbudget in Northern Ireland is not good
OL,10,Fenough for the people of Northern
OL,11,FIreland or the public services that
OL,12,Fthey deserve," he said.
OL,14,F"And that's before you deal with
OL,15,Ftrying to ensure that these cliff
OL,16,Fedges, when it comes to financial
OL,17,Fstability, don't emerge year after
OL,18,Fyear after year.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@NO]vD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G19/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41120
SC,0020
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,F"And that takes some longer-term
OL,8,Fdecisions and more trying, systemic
OL,9,Fdecisions that I hope this government
OL,10,Fwill ensure are the product of the
OL,11,Fwork we've already engaged in."
OL,13,FWith a number of issues on Sir Chris'
OL,14,Fin-tray, including a budget crisis at
OL,15,FStormont and contentious Troubles
OL,16,FLegacy legislation, the confident and
OL,17,Fmedia-savvy MP faces a big task in his
OL,18,Ffirst Cabinet-level role.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@_O]
