OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FSir Chris has become famed for his
OL,8,Flarger-than-life parliamentary
OL,9,Fappearances and creative analogies, as
OL,10,Fwell as being unafraid to speak out on
OL,11,Fpolicy.
OL,13,FHe was born in Cardiff and before
OL,14,Fentering politics served as an
OL,15,FAnglican priest, a career he left due
OL,16,Fto the Church of England's position on
OL,17,Fhomosexuality.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G21/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41122
SC,0022
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FAn experienced parliamentarian, he was
OL,8,Ffirst elected in 2001 and served as a
OL,9,FParliamentary private secretary (PPS)
OL,10,Fto Labour heavyweights Charlie
OL,11,FFalconer and Harriet Harman.
OL,13,FHe became a junior minister under
OL,14,FGordon Brown in 2008, serving as
OL,15,Fdeputy leader of the House of Commons.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G22/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41123
SC,0023
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FIn Labour's years in opposition, he
OL,8,Fheld various shadow ministerial
OL,9,Fpositions, but resigned from the
OL,10,Fshadow cabinet in 2016 in protest at
OL,11,FJeremy Corbyn's leadership and his
OL,12,Fhandling of the Brexit campaign.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G23/26
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
