OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,412,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41124
SC,0024
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F411A1784661517
OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FHe was a loud voice in the Remain
OL,8,Fcampaign and subsequent parliamentary
OL,9,Fdebates, saying Russian president
OL,10,FVladimir Putin had ordered
OL,11,Finterference in the referendum, and
OL,12,Fcalling clauses in the government's
OL,13,FEuropean Union (Withdrawal) Bill, "the
OL,14,Fbiggest peace time power grab" over
OL,15,FParliament in 100 years.
OL,17,FSir Chris ran to be Commons Speaker in
OL,18,F2019, but was beaten by party
OL,19,Fcolleague Sir Lindsay Hoyle.
OL,26,@uD@cOUvD@^O]
