OL,3,CNew NI Secretary on 'daunting' role
OL,4,Cand the 'Bette Midler' position of
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FSince Labour's return to Government,
OL,8,Fhe served as junior minister in the
OL,9,Fculture, media and sport department
OL,10,Fand in the department of science,
OL,11,Finnovation and technology, as well
OL,12,Fbusiness and trade.
OL,14,FSir Chris was knighted in the 2023 New
OL,15,FYear Honours for political and public
OL,16,Fservice.
OL,18,FCatch up with the latest UTV Live on
